# DEP Metadata Guard

**Never edit the `dep:` YAML frontmatter block directly.** Use these CLI commands instead:

| Action | Command |
|---|---|
| Set metadata fields | `dep set <file> --type reference --confidence high --root .` |
| Bump last_verified | `dep bump <file> --root .` |
| Add/remove tags | `dep tag <file> --add cli --root .` |
| Manage links | `dep link <file> --target other.md --rel TEACHES --root .` |
| Bulk bump | `dep bump --all --lifecycle STALE --root .` |

You may freely edit the **markdown body content** below the frontmatter. Only the `dep:` metadata block is managed by CLI.
